78
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:40,564
''Why am l longing?
Why is it raining?''

79
00:10:41,207 --> 00:10:45,735
''Whom am l missing?''

80
00:10:47,613 --> 00:10:50,582
''Why am l yearning...?''

81
00:10:59,625 --> 00:11:01,991
What are you thinking of, son?

82
00:11:03,629 --> 00:11:04,926
Of you.

83
00:11:05,298 --> 00:11:11,066
Of me? l'm a thing of the past now.
Think of the days to come.

84
00:11:11,437 --> 00:11:14,600
Don't avoid the issue.
You brought me to my home.

85
00:11:15,074 --> 00:11:16,735
But surely you have a home too.

86
00:11:16,976 --> 00:11:18,944
You haven't talked about it
till today.

87
00:11:19,378 --> 00:11:22,347
Yes. And that's strange, isn't it?
l had totally forgotten.

88
00:11:23,316 --> 00:11:29,619
You have reminded me that l too
had a home once.

89
00:11:31,357 --> 00:11:37,159
but so much time has gone by...
that l didn't even think of it.

90
00:11:38,064 --> 00:11:41,033
lt's only your voice
that echoes in my ears.

91
