When l'm sad, l go to this place
l'm taking you to.

243
00:27:49,067 --> 00:27:52,366
What do you do when you're sad?
- But l'm never sad.

244
00:27:54,806 --> 00:27:57,707
You will be sad
when you're lonely.

245
